data.description: Check out this adorable two story home on a nice cul-de-sac in Chubbuck! This home offers over 2000 square feet and 4 bed and 2 full/2 half baths. The cozy front porch gives an inviting feeling to the entrance of the home. Entering the house, you will find a spacious living room ready for you to make your own. The living room leads into a clean and spacious dining room and kitchen. With new flooring in the kitchen, beautiful wood cabinets, and a large area for a table, you can easily entertain guests. The washer and dryer hookups are located on the main level with storage space and cabinets. A beautiful master bedroom with high ceilings and shelf space is on the upper floor. There is a full walk in closet, with en suite in the master bedroom along with two other bedrooms and a full bathroom. Down the stairs is a fully finished basement with a bedroom and family room. The backyard is fully fenced with an established yard and sprinkler system.
